{"data":[{"id":561767883,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"959df776b9ad5d55043cf942a0424832","url_token":"miji100","name":"水陌轻寒","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-58ef481c290cf9580a5efcc926c8c5a5_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-58ef481c290cf9580a5efcc926c8c5a5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/959df776b9ad5d55043cf942a0424832","user_type":"people","headline":"也许我们明天就相遇，也许只能在两个宇宙里平行~","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561767883","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545998209,"updated_time":1545998209,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e哥德巴赫被证明了，题主立功了！他继承了民科的光荣的传统。高斯、伽罗华、欧拉、拉格朗日在这一刻灵魂附体！题主代表了民科悠久的历史和传统，在这一刻他不是一个人在战斗，他不是一个人！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560629793,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"30168e4f2357ce9f02297201de098255","url_token":"liu-gen-yue","name":"亘越","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-eac7b9f945c028503cebe5416523bda2_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-eac7b9f945c028503cebe5416523bda2_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/30168e4f2357ce9f02297201de098255","user_type":"people","headline":"目不识丁","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560629793","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545875265,"updated_time":1545875265,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e就可以直接博士生毕业。不，可以直接评上教授。不，可以直接拿菲尔兹奖。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不，这不可能。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559717513,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"60fc433e9e2a3c74d1cb8091a3a4b66a","url_token":"wu-hen-65-60","name":"吴痕","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/6278d5b94f80ac775d15ca5494850006_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/6278d5b94f80ac775d15ca5494850006_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/60fc433e9e2a3c74d1cb8091a3a4b66a","user_type":"people","headline":"爱买小米产品，容易闲扯辨舌，心态厄尔尼诺","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559717513","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545754519,"updated_time":1545754519,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":18,"content":"\u003cp\u003e会。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e前提是：\u003cb\u003e真的证明了\u003c/b\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果有高中生做到了，那么他的论文深度已经足以保证他的数学功底能够满足“XX大学数学系”的要求。任何成果都不是无本之木，若干年前的年纪轻轻就为群论做出开拓性成果的伽罗瓦同志，也不是自己端着一堆初等数学教材在那里玩玄学，人家可是学习了大量的高等数学知识（只是人家掌握有点快……）。因此如果存在这样牛逼的高中生，他的成果大概率不是在一堆初高中数学课本中达成的，而是来自于提前掌握了非常高端的数学工具，甚至洞悉当前数论研究的前沿。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e或者非要说是不世出的天才一个人凭借初等数学知识推出来一个媲美现代数学的理论体系，这个……开心就好。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559820267,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"22013139469948a48a6983a22b362c3c","url_token":"bj365","name":"空一格","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-16bff4cd9b634f213e42a85d121b3c86_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-16bff4cd9b634f213e42a85d121b3c86_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/22013139469948a48a6983a22b362c3c","user_type":"people","headline":"科技创造财富，知识点亮人生。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559820267","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545785674,"updated_time":1545785674,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":29,"content":"\u003cp\u003e酿希匹，别说保送清华北大上研了，当教授都没问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e别说在清北当教授了，哈佛数学系都要过来挖你！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e诺贝尔奖里没有数学奖，但是数学有\u003cb\u003e费尔兹奖\u003c/b\u003e啊！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e前些年有个俄罗斯怪才证明了庞加莱猜想，被授予了费尔兹奖。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你要是证明了哥德巴赫猜想，给你授三次费尔兹奖也不为过啊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你即使得了一次费尔兹奖，你这倍子直接拿下了，还保什么送啊？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561366667,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"9537d5520b80eef1771e7bfef8982381","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561366667","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545962477,"updated_time":1545962477,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不光会被清北保送 而且还会拿菲尔兹奖 可能开辟了新的数学方向 改写数学史 连带着数学的n个分支的发展 还有终身教授 金钱荣誉地位 走向人生巅峰 成为历史人物！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560474011,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"aea5bb74cdc9c44e0b2b6a450a870459","url_token":"zhi-zhang-shao-nian-55-68","name":"起个名真费劲","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/aea5bb74cdc9c44e0b2b6a450a870459","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560474011","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545840654,"updated_time":1545840898,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":48,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不管题主是否证明出了哥德巴赫猜想，都会有人支持你，因为谁没年少轻狂过，你还年轻，有的是可能，有的是时间。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你的证明正确，皆大欢喜，如果你的证明不正确，希望你也不要放弃对数学的热爱，毕竟冰冷的高山，不是那么好爬。愿你以后再回想当初的自己，能不悔当初，一笑了之\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e来自一个知乎小透明的首次长(？)答\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e求轻喷\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e感激不尽\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560661653,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560661653","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545877651,"updated_time":1545877651,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e没有想到这个问题引起了不少关注，甚至不少回答者做出了各色各样的回答，当然无论嘲讽，讥笑，批判，鼓励，原本以为只是个脑洞题，没想到确实是有人真实的内心问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我无法就这个问题给出回答，但是可以反过来给予一定的思考:进入清华北大，数学方面就能做出巨大的成就吗，答案自然是否定的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e今年刚好是中科院20周年庆，科院回顾了相关领域的成果，摘取部分如下:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e席南华对仿射A型Weyl群证明了Lusztig关于基环的猜想，成为国际上很多后续工作的基础之一\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e周向宇带领研究生解决了多复变中的“经典问题”最优L2延拓问题、证明了Demailly强开性猜想，在美国《数学评论》上被评论为“近年来多复变与代数几何领域最伟大的成就之一”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“新生代”数学家田野首次给出7个千禧数学问题之一“椭圆曲线BSD猜想”的重要线索\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e人称“论证骑士”的孙斌勇与李文威对朗兰兹纲领一系列重要问题的探索，以及青年学者黄飞敏在玻尔兹曼方程的流体力学方面，都取得了重要的突破\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e冯康独立于西方创始了有限元方法，在国际上首次提出基于辛几何原理计算哈密尔顿体系的新方法\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e袁亚湘等最早使用子空间技术分析计算方法，相继提出了子空间共轭梯度法、非线性优化子空间法与子空间拟牛顿法等方法。该方法被称为Dai-Yuan方法，并且与FR方法、HS方法、PRP方法并列，被认为是“四个主要方法”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e张平和黄飞敏团队证明了各向异性不可压缩Navier-Stokes方程整体适定性；证明了在黎曼解这一重要情形下Boltzmann方程的极限是可压缩Euler方程\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e插一个故事（我听彭实戈讲过一个故事:他高中的时候正好哥猜流行，他的许多同学那时候也兴致勃勃，想要在这方面一展身手，但大多数后来就放弃了，后来他知识青年下乡，经常捧着一本苏联某数学课本看，周围没有几个懂数学的，不会的问题经常是跑几个村子去找能够解答的人讨论）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e观看他们的履历不难发现，绝大多数不是清北出身，当然北大出身自然也有做出了很多巨大成就的，但是无一例外不是在各自领域深耕数十年，现代数学的庞杂性远超过很多人的理解，提及数学绝不是只有哥猜甚至是囿于基础数学领域，大概率的结果是对于非基础数学领域的其他数学工作者，相关领域的突破要比哥猜来的重要些。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果真要证明自己的价值，不是非要攀登数学的几座顶峰，那上面容易缺氧窒息而亡，不如先爬几座山头，锻炼一下身体，在决定是否要那些方向走。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559993656,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"bdc4123e8980c20b2109e00619d8fbea","url_token":"chen-xiang-yu-99-80","name":"陈向隅","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-feed5f9947f12a2bdd3e5c906597c1ef_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-feed5f9947f12a2bdd3e5c906597c1ef_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/bdc4123e8980c20b2109e00619d8fbea","user_type":"people","headline":"我们背抵黑暗，只为守护光明。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559993656","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4fcc3098aef43f4cccc0193a77dd7b77_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545799965,"updated_time":1545799972,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":57,"content":"\u003cp\u003e作为一个纯天然无添加的数学白痴，我甚至去悄咪咪百度了一下啥是哥德巴赫.......\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0107783cb5736be4d2306b34445e92b8_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"120\" data-rawheight=\"120\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"120\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='120'%20height='120'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"120\" data-rawheight=\"120\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"120\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0107783cb5736be4d2306b34445e92b8_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然鹅这并没有什么卵用因为我压根就没看懂百度百科到底在说啥。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4fcc3098aef43f4cccc0193a77dd7b77_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"214\" data-rawheight=\"154\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"214\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='214'%20height='154'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"214\" data-rawheight=\"154\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"214\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4fcc3098aef43f4cccc0193a77dd7b77_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e我是jio得吧，既然答主都能想着去证明它了，那数学起码还是不错的。就算到时候真的证明失败也没关系，上个211什么的一样可以继续追梦嘛。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然还是要祝福一下，毕竟万一真的证明了，全世界的数学家可以少掉多少根头发啊。23333。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b312de00b55a0b3a3fb19f780bb836a4_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"124\" data-rawheight=\"116\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"124\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='124'%20height='116'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"124\" data-rawheight=\"116\" data-size=\"normal\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"124\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b312de00b55a0b3a3fb19f780bb836a4_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":557774031,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fbc1661039fe84e3d0eae8ee359d98e5","url_token":"reciprocity","name":"Reciprocity","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fbc1661039fe84e3d0eae8ee359d98e5","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/557774031","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545527876,"updated_time":1545527876,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":20,"content":"\u003cp\u003e1. 如果你只用初等数论知识完成的证明，建议放弃。因为证明错的概率是99.999999%，话说回来，即使你的证明没有问题，一个很严肃的问题是你很难找到一个大学数学老师来花时间验证这个东西。民科或许愿意，但民科一样无法获得主流学术界的认同。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2. 如果你的英文还可以，建议将其翻译成英文，挂在arxiv上。挂上去之后你对这个享有完全的著作权，不必担心抄袭问题，同时向国际顶级期刊投稿，如Ann. Math, JAMS, Acta Math等等。怀尔斯的费马大定理的证明就是在Ann. Math. 上发表的哦。一旦在这种期刊上发表，就宣告了你的证明的正确性。而不是像其他答主贴图一样，发表在国内水杂志上，并没有任何卵用\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561735015,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"67c5aaf9a33281525d70153377c90541","url_token":"qing-nian-bu-wen-yi-10","name":"不学习毋宁死","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ca5e9da0a43ece52bdafdb848098b94_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ca5e9da0a43ece52bdafdb848098b94_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/67c5aaf9a33281525d70153377c90541","user_type":"people","headline":"我这么帅居然只是一个小号","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561735015","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0731a1ea0c454933ea052b1dd63f126f_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545994378,"updated_time":1545996673,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":19,"content":"\u003cp\u003e感觉你们都忽略了另外一个可能性。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实题主是穿越过来的，那个时候已经有人证明了，刚好他看到了，所以……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e问下题主，你买返程票了吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e刚刚看了题主的主页，有了一些新的看法\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-30a641aeecd860663a4e1fa602536bc4_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-cd47caac129dcc68391afe4a14392229_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-30a641aeecd860663a4e1fa602536bc4_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-cd47caac129dcc68391afe4a14392229_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-30a641aeecd860663a4e1fa602536bc4_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-30a641aeecd860663a4e1fa602536bc4_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e这是他比较早的动态。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e关于四面体的问题\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后再一个题目下\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-bdfec62855c1c934dd480214b0acc5fe_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-cd4bdf5c6a669f7e62f6424201bcfb07_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-bdfec62855c1c934dd480214b0acc5fe_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-cd4bdf5c6a669f7e62f6424201bcfb07_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-bdfec62855c1c934dd480214b0acc5fe_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-bdfec62855c1c934dd480214b0acc5fe_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个题目下的回答是哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们可以猜测这个问题起源他对四面体的研究。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e再看看时间，最开始是三个月前，也就是九月份左右\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们高中尤其是高三九月份有哪些大事儿呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e奥赛。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们做一个大胆的猜测\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e事情是这样的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主应该高中在读。学校可能还不错，毕竟能组织奥数的应该还行。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主的成绩应该比较偏科。数学应该是强项。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其他科应该不行。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以题主高中前面两年把时间都搭在了奥数上面。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然而事与愿违。九月份的奥赛滑铁卢了（我们假设他是有拿奖的能力的）。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以经过深思熟虑之后，觉得自己应该是没戏了，其他科不行，数学也挂了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e怎么办呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e怎么办呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个时候突然想起了比赛试卷上一道关于四面体的题目，题主应该没做出来。可能的是这一题耽误了他很多时间，让他比赛失利。于是他就想把这条解出来 然后到处咨询，最后从同学哪里得知，知乎是一个985遍地走，211不如狗的高层次学术研讨平台。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以他看到了那个歌猜。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e转念一想，这个以前老师有提到过，感觉应该能搞出来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e于是他就开始到处查阅相关知识点。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e通过时间线可以看出\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他花了一个月差找资料。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e再两个月前还有一个七七八八的动态，我想在那个时候他应该有思路了，所以来放松一下。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后几天前，他把问题搞出来了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对于这个问题，我敢肯定，他的证明肯定用了其他专业的知识，不是正面回答的，比如说我们要测体积可以用排水法。所以他才说他的方法别人看不懂。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那么对于这种情况，他的证明基本没戏，就算是对的，哪怕若干年之后被后入证明是对的，他在现在也没什么用。因为专业的期刊不会承认的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么我会有这样的想法，因为那些年我也是这样子的。那年物理奥数挂了之后，心灰意冷，感觉整个人都不好了。其他科成绩每一科都是七十分左右（包括语数英）。不过经过短暂的思考之后我觉得好好学习，奋力一搏。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后………………\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e等会儿再说，工头叫我过去把搅拌机弄一下。毕竟我是我们工程队最有文化的。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561297093,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e26034c914d0115722adf3c211325ef0","url_token":"sanshiliuhaoji","name":